com.here.android.mpa.customlocation2

Class CLE2MultiPolylineGeometry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.customlocation2.CLE2Geometry
      • com.here.android.mpa.customlocation2.CLE2MultiPolylineGeometry

  • public final class CLE2MultiPolylineGeometry
extends CLE2Geometry
    Specifies a user-defined multi polyline geometry. A multi polyline geometry represent a list of GeoPolyline.
